JD 7:

Core responsibilities:
• Lead and support strategic sourcing for assigned financial categories from spend analysis through contract execution.
• Manage contract creation, approvals, and vendor negotiations.
• Identify process improvements and prepare cost/benefit analyses for sourcing decisions.
• Coach junior procurement staff on category processes and negotiation strategies.

